---
title: Herbed Parmesan Pinwheels Serves 2 | with Caramelized Onions
description: Tonight you can look forward to savoury puff pastry filled with smoky-sweet caramelized onions, parsley, thyme and melted white cheddar cheese. These flaky handheld bites are the perfect pre-dinner snack!
